asset.hookText: http://www.skis.com/Rossignol-Taipan-AmpTek-Snowboard-2013/280936P,default,pd.html  The Rossignol Taipan Snowboard has won several awards from Transworld the past two years and is going to continue to build that record. The sick, smooth ride of the Rossignol Taipan Snowboard proves it time and time again. Designed with versatility in mind The Taipan Snowboard features the AmpTek All-Mountain camber giving you the freedom to rip the hardpack on one run and slash the pow on the next without sacrificing an ounce of performance. AmpTek All-Mountain 60% rocker / 40% camber for more control and stability. The Wood 6420 core features 6420 cross-weave fiberglass wrapped around a vertically laminated wood core that gives you durability and performance without breaking the bank. The Rossignol Taipan is designed for intermediate to advanced riders; this board can take you anywhere, believe us, try it out for yourself.
